text: OK, so this is Jeffrey style happy so it cannot be 100% happy but.
I think something that makes me really happy.
And if I'm alone, it's easy to have these negative thoughts a lot.
Something that makes me happy or relieved and just like.

Is when I go back to school after the long weekend and I get to see my friends and everyone is happy to see me and then I realize like all my negative thoughts are just in my own head and I'm so grateful for my friends.
It makes me happy that they are good friends, too.
